      <title>在诉讼中，新的尸检结果将德克萨斯州囚犯的死亡与极端高温联系起来</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/30/nx-s1-5049791/amid-lawsuits-new-autopsies-link-texas-prisoner-deaths-to-extreme-heat</link>
